{"tid":1660652,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Steve Bannon 談及香港人不要太有自信過人權法。","createTime":"2019-10-17T15:30:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T18:13:18.000Z","uid":322446,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8969dabd7cb01dd30cd07ec79148058766dd34f1","tid":1660652,"uid":322446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T15:30:49.000Z","msg":"睇片<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vSEhHcFMRbo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvSEhHcFMRbo&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAScuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=72b10931\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vSEhHcFMRbo</a><br />\n<br />\nSteven Bannon 對話中透露香港人只要堅持五大訴求，不要做一些過激的行為，例如香港獨立，這只會讓中國有籍口出師有名。更透露美國華爾街有很多利益主義者𣎴斷游說國會議員 不要過人權法等等......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n852郵報版本<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0UkhN_sN92U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0UkhN_sN92U&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAScuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=cf6c0c30\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0UkhN_sN92U</a><br />\n<br />\nSteve Bannon 重申 香港人一定堅持到底，要看着時勢轉變，隨機應變。"},{"pid":"c8447cb2ff8e65e1cadab045f5d58fd4051e3035","tid":1660652,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T15:31:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W04Z2Gp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW04Z2Gp.jpg&h=e79a1d2a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d4691ff77847d05fae06f37495e9864f168f8595","tid":1660652,"uid":270563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T15:36:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7db585951ee4c2bf51b6f94aeaa258ab3c2559d8","tid":1660652,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T15:42:50.000Z","msg":"一日未到最後 都唔知結局<br />\n要堅持 五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"